# Component Guidelines

## Component Architecture

### Component Organization
- [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui) - Reusable UI components (buttons, inputs, etc.)
- [src/components/NavBar/](mdc:src/components/NavBar) - Navigation components
- [src/components/TopBar/](mdc:src/components/TopBar) - Top bar components
- [src/components/Home/](mdc:src/components/Home) - Home page specific components
- Individual component files for specific features

### Component Structure
```typescript
// src/components/ExampleComponent/ExampleComponent.tsx
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils';

interface ExampleComponentProps {
  title: string;
  children?: React.ReactNode;
  className?: string;
}

export default function ExampleComponent({
  title,
  children,
  className
}: ExampleComponentProps) {
  return (
    <div className={cn('base-styles', className)}>
      <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold">{title}</h2>
      {children}
    </div>
  );
}
```

